Subject: Wazuh - SIEM Integration Problem [Roofstacks]
Description:
Hello Team,

The customer is using the Wazuh SIEM solution. Although they have completed the SIEM integration in Appliance -> SIEM Integration, they mentioned that the logs are not sending to the SIEM. What could be causing this issue? How can we resolve it?

Server Version: 5.9.4.0
Solution_Comment__c: customer network is blocking the traffic on the port 514
